itor() \u00b7 flow_map \u00b7 RTT EWMA</span></div><div style='background:#0c1f3a;border:1px solid #58a6ff;border-radius:5px;padding:8px;margin-bottom:7px'><span style='color:#58a6ff;font-weight:bold'>T2 \u2014 Gradient Estimator (500ms)</span><br><span style='color:#8b949e;font-size:11px'>G(t) = 0.6\u00b7\u2207dr/30 + 0.4\u00b7\u2207bl/300</span></div><div style='background:#0d1f0d;border:1px solid #3fb950;border-radius:5px;padding:8px;margin-bottom:10px'><span style='color:#3fb950;font-weight:bold'>T3 \u2014 AIMD Policy (~5s)</span><br><span style='color:#8b949e;font-size:11px'>HEAVY: target\u00d70.9 \u00b7 LIGHT: target+0.5ms</span></div><div style='border-top:1px solid #21262d;padding-top:8px'><div style='color:#bc8cff;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:5px'>Novel Contributions</div><div style='color:#8b949e;font-size:11px'><span style='color:#58a6ff'>C1</span> Gradient fusion \u2207dr+\u2207bl+\u2207rtt<br><span style='color:#bc8cff'>C2</span> Predictive [PREDICTIVE] tag<br><span style='color:#d29922'>C3</span> eBPF elephant/mice quantum adapt<br><span style='color:#3fb950'>C4</span> Three-timescale on stock Linux</div></div></div>"}, "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "dfijmkbfrcow0d"}}]}